<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Daily Test</title>

<style>

body{
font-family:"Microsoft JhengHei",sans-serif;
background:#f6f6f6;
padding:50px;
}

.day-section{
max-width:1200px;
margin:auto;
display:flex;
flex-direction:column;
gap:80px;
}

.day-item{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
gap:50px;
align-items:center;
background:white;
padding:30px;
border-radius:20px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}

.day-item.reverse{
direction:rtl;
}

.day-item.reverse .day-text{
direction:ltr;
}

.day-item img{
width:100%;
border-radius:15px;
}

.day-text h3{
font-size:32px;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.day-text p{
font-size:18px;
line-height:1.8;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

.day-item,
.day-item.reverse{
display:block;
}

.day-item img{
margin-bottom:20px;
}

}

</style>

</head>
<body>

<h1 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:60px;">
每日行程測試
</h1>

<div class="day-section">

<div class="day-item">

<img src="Daily/day01-vienna-window.png">

<div class="day-text">

<h3>Day 1｜啟程飛往維也納</h3>

<p>
搭乘豪華客機前往奧地利首都，
展開璀璨12天的中歐旅程。
</p>

</div>

</div>

<div class="day-item reverse">

<img src="Daily/day02-wachau.jpg">

<div class="day-text">

<h3>Day 2｜瓦豪河谷</h3>

<p>
沿著多瑙河航行，
欣賞世界遺產瓦豪河谷與梅爾克修道院。
</p>

</div>

</div>

<div class="day-item">

<img src="Daily/day03-hallstatt.jpg">

<div class="day-text">

<h3>Day 3｜哈修塔特</h3>

<p>
漫步世界最美湖畔小鎮，
感受阿爾卑斯湖區的迷人風景。
</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
